T1  - Average size of plants in manufacturing and capital intensity: A cross-country analysis by industry
AU  - Banerji, Ranadev
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 5
IS  - 2
SP  - 155
EP  - 166
PY  - 1978
DA  - 1978/06/01/
